StmtSimple.StatementText: INSERT INTO #Bid_BidRank(CSKID, CurrentRank, UpdateDate, FinalBid, QualityScore,MinBid) SELECT br.CSKID, br.CurrentRank, @now, bi.FinalBid,br.QualityScore,br.MinBid FROM dbo.Staging_BidRank br JOIN Bid bi ON bi.CSKID = br.CSKID AND br.CurrentRank IS NOT NULL

MERGE dbo.CSKeywordsRankInfo AS target USING (SELECT CSKID, CurrentRank, UpdateDate, FinalBid, QualityScore,MinBid FROM #Bid_BidRank ) AS source ON (target.CSKID = source.CSKID) WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET CurrentRank = source.CurrentRank, Bid = source.FinalBid, LGRank = (CASE WHEN source.CurrentRank = 0 THEN target.LGRank ELSE source.CurrentRank END), LGBid = (CASE WHEN source.CurrentRank = 0 THEN target.LGBid ELSE source.FinalBid END), LGDate = (CASE WHEN source.CurrentRank = 0 THEN target.LGDate ELSE source.UpdateDate END), QualityScore = source.QualityScore, MinBid = source.MinBid, UpdateDate = source.UpdateDate WHEN NOT MATCHED BY TARGET THEN INSERT (CSKID, CurrentRank, UpdateDate, Bid, LGRank, LGBid, LGDate,QualityScore,MinBid) VALUES (CSKID, CurrentRank, UpdateDate, FinalBid, CurrentRank, FinalBid, UpdateDate, QualityScore,MinBid) OUTPUT inserted.CSKID,inserted.CurrentRank,inserted.Bid,inserted.MinBid INTO #output(CSKID,CurrentRank,Bid,MinBid);
--SELECT COUNT(1) FROM #output --SELECT COUNT(1) FROM #Bid_BidRank

[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[MinBid] as [target].[MinBid] = [Expr1013],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[LGRank] as [target].[LGRank] = [Expr1014],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[LGDate] as [target].[LGDate] = [Expr1015],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[UpdateDate] as [target].[UpdateDate] = RaiseIfNullUpdate([Expr1017]),[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[Bid] as [target].[Bid] = [Expr1018],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[QualityScore] as [target].[QualityScore] = [Expr1019],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[LGBid] as [target].[LGBid] = [Expr1020],[SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[CurrentRank] as [target].[CurrentRank] = [Expr1021]

CASE WHEN [Action1012]=(4) THEN [#Bid_BidRank].[CurrentRank] ELSE CASE WHEN [#Bid_BidRank].[CurrentRank]=(0.00) THEN [SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[LGRank] as [target].[LGRank] ELSE [#Bid_BidRank].[CurrentRank] END END

CASE WHEN [Action1012]=(4) THEN [#Bid_BidRank].[UpdateDate] ELSE CASE WHEN [#Bid_BidRank].[CurrentRank]=(0.00) THEN [SearchIgnite].[dbo].[CSKeywordsRankInfo].[LGDate] as [target].[LGDate] ELSE [#Bid_BidRank].[UpdateDate] END END

StmtSimple.StatementText: UPDATE t SET RankChanged = br.RankChanged FROM #output t JOIN dbo.Staging_BidRank br ON br.CSKID = t.CSKID
INSERT INTO dbo.CSKeywordsRankInfo5daysHist(CSKID, UpdateDate, CurrentRank, Bid, MinBid) SELECT CSKID, @Now, CurrentRank, Bid, MinBid FROM #output WHERE RankChanged = 1
